ACCOMPLISHMENT ON ANTI-ILLEGAL DRUGS (Buy-bust) OPERATION:
At about 7:00 PM of September 2, 2025, MDET of Titay MPS led by PMAJ ARNOLD A ESPARES, ACOP conducted drug Buy-bust operation at Barangay Dalangin, Titay, Zamboanga Sibugay Province that resulted on the arrest of one male individual and confiscation of the following items:
a. Five (5) pcs small heat-sealed transparent plastic sachets containing white crystalline substance suspected to be shabu with an estimated weight of 1 gram with SDP of Php 6,800.00;
b. One (1) pc white paper;
c. One (1) pc small box labeled as GRS;
d. One (1) pc disposable lighter color blue;
e. Two (2) pcs Genuine twenty-peso bills with serial numbers AC603637 and CG902888; and
f. One (1) pc Five-Hundred-peso bill (Marked Money) with serial number MC002895.
